             was indicted for <rs id="t17991204-49-off266" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17991204-49-off266" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17991204-49-off266" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17991204-49-cd267" type="crimeDate">16th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17991204-49-off266 t17991204-49-cd267"></join>, thirteen penny pieces, and ten halfpence
            </rs>, the property of 
               <persName id="t17991204-49-victim436" type="victimName">
                  Peter 
                  Priest
               <interp inst="t17991204-49-victim436" type="surname" value="Priest"></interp>
